---

<Layout title="Calgary Airbnb Management | 10-15%" description="Calgary Airbnb management for Downtown, Beltline, Stampede Park, and airport area properties. Dynamic pricing and guest screening. 10-15% fees. Free estimate.">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1><span class="highlight">Calgary Airbnb Management</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Expert property management in Canada's energy capital</p>

      <div class="hero-stats">
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-number">$3,200+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Avg Monthly Revenue</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-number">75%+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Avg Occupancy Rate</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-number">10-15%</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Management Fee</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">See How Much Your Calgary Property Can Earn</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section neighborhoods">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Calgary Neighborhoods We Serve</h2>
        <p>From downtown to the foothills</p>
      </div>
      <div class="neighborhoods-grid">
        {neighborhoods.map(n => (
          <div class="neighborhood-card">
            <h3>{n.icon} {n.name}</h3>
            <p>{n.description}</p>
            <div class="avg-revenue">Avg Revenue: {n.revenue}</div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bylaws-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Calgary Short-Term Rental Rules</h2>
        <p>What Calgary property owners need to know</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bylaws-content">
        <div class="bylaws-grid">
          <div class="bylaw-card">
            <h3>Business License Required</h3>
            <p>Calgary requires a <a href="/blog/calgary-airbnb-short-term-rental-rules-2026">business license</a> for short-term rental operators. The application process is straightforward and we can guide you through it.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bylaw-card">
            <h3>No Principal Residence Rule</h3>
            <p>Unlike many Ontario cities like <a href="/downtown-toronto-airbnb-management">Toronto</a>, Calgary does not restrict STRs to principal residences only. Investment properties can be used for short-term rentals.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bylaw-card">
            <h3>Safety Requirements</h3>
            <p>Properties must meet fire and safety standards including smoke detectors, carbon monoxide detectors, and fire extinguishers.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bylaw-card">
            <h3>Tourism Levy</h3>
            <p>Calgary collects a tourism levy on short-term accommodations. Airbnb typically collects and remits this automatically on your behalf.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section why-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="why-content">
        <h2>The Calgary Stampede Advantage</h2>
        <p>Calgary's famous Stampede brings over 1 million visitors annually, creating exceptional earning potential for Airbnb hosts. Properties near Stampede Park can command 3-4x normal rates during the 10-day event.</p>
        <p>Beyond Stampede, Calgary enjoys consistent demand from oil & gas business travelers, convention attendees, and tourists heading to Banff and the Rocky Mountains. Our <a href="/services/full-airbnb-management" style="color: #C9A961;">full-service management</a> handles everything so you can earn passively.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="airport-stats">
        <div class="airport-stat">
          <div class="number">1M+</div>
          <div class="label">Annual Stampede Visitors</div>
        </div>
        <div class="airport-stat">
          <div class="number">3-4x</div>
          <div class="label">Stampede Rate Premium</div>
        </div>
        <div class="airport-stat">
          <div class="number">4M+</div>
          <div class="label">Annual Banff Visitors</div>
        </div>
        <div class="airport-stat">
          <div class="number">365</div>
          <div class="label">Days of Business Travel</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section services-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Full-Service Calgary Management</h2>
        <p>Everything included at 10-15%</p>
      </div>
      <div class="services-grid">
        {services.map(service => (
          <div class="service-item">
            <span class="service-check">‚úì</span>
            <span>{service}</span>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section other-areas">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Explore Our Other Service Areas</h2>
        <p>We manage properties across Canada</p>
      </div>
      <div class="areas-grid">
        <a href="/downtown-toronto-airbnb-management" class="area-link">
          <span>Downtown Toronto</span>
          <span class="arrow">‚Üí</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/niagara-falls-airbnb-management" class="area-link">
          <span>Niagara Falls</span>
          <span class="arrow">‚Üí</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/kitchener-airbnb-management" class="area-link">
          <span>Kitchener</span>
          <span class="arrow">‚Üí</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/waterloo-airbnb-management" class="area-link">
          <span>Waterloo</span>
          <span class="arrow">‚Üí</span>
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="areas-cta">View all <a href="/locations">service areas</a> or learn more about our <a href="/services">services</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Own a Calgary Property?</h2>
        <p>Get a free analysis showing how much your downtown, Beltline, or Stampede-area property could earn with Airbnb.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-large">Get Your Free Analysis</a>
        <p class="cta-note">Free consultation ‚Ä¢ No obligation ‚Ä¢ Results in 24 hours</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-background-alt) 0%, var(--color-background) 100%);
    padding: 8rem 0 6rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: -2rem;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .hero .highlight { color: var(--color-primary); }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .hero-stats {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 4rem;
    margin: 3rem 0;
  }

  .stat { text-align: center; }
  .stat-number { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-primary); }
  .stat-label { color: var(--color-text-light); font-size: 0.9rem; }

  .neighborhoods-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .neighborhood-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    border-top: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .neighborhood-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); }
  .neighborhood-card h3 { font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .neighborhood-card p { color: var(--color-text-light); margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; }

  .avg-revenue {
    background: var(--color-background-alt);
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .bylaws-section { background: var(--color-background-alt); }

  .bylaws-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .bylaw-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .bylaw-card h3 { color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.25rem; }
  .bylaw-card p { color: var(--color-text-light); line-height: 1.7; }

  .why-section {
    background: var(--color-primary-dark);
    color: white;
  }

  .why-section .container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .why-content h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .why-content p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  }

  .airport-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .airport-stat {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .airport-stat .number {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #C9A961;
  }

  .airport-stat .label {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
  }

  .services-section { background: var(--color-background-alt); }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .service-item {
    background: white;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .service-check { color: var(--color-primary); font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; }

  .cta-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, var(--color-primary-dark) 100%);
    padding: 5rem 0;
    text-align: center;
    color: white;
  }

  .cta-content h2 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .cta-content > p { font-size: 1.25rem; opacity: 0.9; margin-bottom: 2rem; max-width: 700px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
  .cta-section .btn { background: white; color: var(--color-primary); }
  .cta-section .btn:hover { background: var(--color-background-alt); }
  .cta-note { margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: 0.95rem; opacity: 0.9; }

  .other-areas { background: var(--color-background); }

  .areas-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .area-link {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    background: white;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 600;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .area-link:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }

  .area-link .arrow { color: var(--color-primary); transition: transform 0.3s ease; }
  .area-link:hover .arrow { transform: translateX(4px); }

  .areas-cta { text-align: center; color: var(--color-text-light); }
  .areas-cta a { color: var(--color-primary); text-decoration: underline; }
  .areas-cta a:hover { color: var(--color-primary-dark); }

  @media (max-width: 968px) {
    .neighborhoods-grid, .services-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .bylaws-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .why-section .container { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .areas-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 576px) {
    .hero-stats { flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem; }
    .neighborhoods-grid, .services-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .areas-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
